snippet.title: Trip - Six One Indie Showcase Trailer
snippet.description: Will you unravel the mysteries that hides in this train? A lot of surprises and colourful characters are waiting for you in this first person retro adventure game! Check out the trailer for Trip for a peek at this surreal world. Trip is coming to PC, and a demo is available now.
